裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　1 　　月　　25　　日\r\n                            書記官  陳柏志","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/STEV/110%2c%e5%ba%97%e5%b0%8f%2c1721%2c20220125%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"STEV,110,店小,1721,20220125,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"店小","JNO":"1721","JDATE":"20220125","JTITLE":"損害賠償"}